11 Replace a string's accent characters with ASCII characters.
 
12 
13 Based on Perl Text::Unaccent from CPAN.
 
14 
15 
16 == French Example
 
17 
18   str = "déjà vu";
 
19   str.unaccent => "deja vu";
 
20 
21 == Greek Example
 
22 
23   str = "νέα" (aka "\x{03AD}\x{03BD}\x{03B1}")
 
24   str.unaccent => "νεα" (aka "\x{03B5}\x{03BD}\x{03B1}")
 
25 
26 =end
 
27 
28 
29 class String
 
30 
31   # Replace a string's accent characters with ASCII characters.
 
32   # 
33   # ==Example
 
34   #   s = "Å Ç ß"
 
35   #   s.unaccent = > "AA C ss"
 
36 
37   def unaccent
 
38     split(//u).map {|c| ACCENTMAP[c] || c }.join("")
 
39   end
 
40
